{"id":195,"parent_id":191,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":195,"title":"Colossians 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Col.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","The Saints are told to be wise in all things—Luke and others greet the Colossians."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.1","order":"03.14.004.21320"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Masters"],", give unto",["i","your"],"servants that which is just and equal; knowing that ye also have a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Master"],"in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.2","order":"03.14.004.21321"},["b","2"],"Continue in prayer, and watch in the same with thanksgiving;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.3","order":"03.14.004.21322"},["b","3"],"Withal praying also for us, that God would open unto us a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"door"],"of utterance, to speak the mystery of Christ, for which I am also in bonds:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.4","order":"03.14.004.21323"},["b","4"],"That I may make it manifest, as I ought to speak."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.5","order":"03.14.004.21324"},["b","5"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Walk"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"wisdom"],"toward them that are without, redeeming the time."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.6","order":"03.14.004.21325"},["b","6"],"Let your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"speech"],["i","be"],"alway with grace, seasoned with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"salt"],", that ye may know how ye ought to answer every man."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.7","order":"03.14.004.21326"},["b","7"],"All my state shall Tychicus declare unto you,",["i","who is"],"a beloved brother, and a faithful minister and fellowservant in the Lord:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.8","order":"03.14.004.21327"},["b","8"],"Whom I have sent unto you for the same purpose, that he might know your estate, and comfort your hearts;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.9","order":"03.14.004.21328"},["b","9"],"With",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Onesimus"],", a faithful and beloved brother, who is",["i","one"],"of you. They shall make known unto you all things which",["i","are done"],"here."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.10","order":"03.14.004.21329"},["b","10"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Aristarchus"],"my fellowprisoner saluteth you, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"Marcus"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sister’s son"],"to Barnabas, (touching whom ye received commandments: if he come unto you, receive him;)"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.11","order":"03.14.004.21330"},["b","11"],"And Jesus, which is called Justus, who are of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"circumcision"],". These only",["i","are my"],"fellowworkers unto the kingdom of God, which have been a comfort unto me."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.12","order":"03.14.004.21331"},["b","12"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Epaphras"],", who is",["i","one"],"of you, a servant of Christ, saluteth you, always labouring fervently for you in prayers, that ye may stand perfect and complete in all the will of God."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.13","order":"03.14.004.21332"},["b","13"],"For I bear him record, that he hath a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"zeal"],"for you, and them",["i","that are"],"in Laodicea, and them in Hierapolis."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.14","order":"03.14.004.21333"},["b","14"],"Luke, the beloved physician, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Demas"],", greet you."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.15","order":"03.14.004.21334"},["b","15"],"Salute the brethren which are in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Laodicea"],", and Nymphas, and the church which is in his house."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.16","order":"03.14.004.21335"},["b","16"],"And when this epistle is read among you, cause that it be read also in the church of the Laodiceans; and that ye likewise read the",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"epistle"]],"from Laodicea."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.17","order":"03.14.004.21336"},["b","17"],"And say to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Archippus"],", Take heed to the ministry which thou hast received in the Lord, that thou fulfil it."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.18","order":"03.14.004.21337"},["b","18"],"The salutation by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"hand"],"of me Paul. Remember my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"bonds"],". Grace",["i","be"],"with you. Amen."]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col.closing.7","order":".000.21380"},[".closing","¶Written from Rome to the Colossians by Tychicus and Onesimus."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.1a","order":"03.14.004.21338"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.5"},"Mal. 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/6.9"},"Eph. 6:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.1b","order":"03.14.004.21340"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/23.8"},"Matt. 23:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.1c","order":"03.14.004.21342"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heaven"},"TG Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.3a","order":"03.14.004.21344"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.9"},"1 Cor. 16:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.5a","order":"03.14.004.21346"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.5b","order":"03.14.004.21348"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"TG Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.6a","order":"03.14.004.21350"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/communication"},"TG Communication"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.6b","order":"03.14.004.21352"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salt"},"TG Salt"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.9a","order":"03.14.004.21354"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.10"},"Philem. 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.10a","order":"03.14.004.21356"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/19.29"},"Acts 19:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.4"},"20:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/27.2"},"27:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.10b","order":"03.14.004.21358"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.37.37-39"},"Acts 15:37 (37–39)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.11"},"2 Tim. 4:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.10c","order":"03.14.004.21360"},["b","10c"],["span.small","GR"],"cousin, kinsman."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.11a","order":"03.14.004.21362"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.12a","order":"03.14.004.21364"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.7.7-8"},"Col. 1:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.23"},"Philem. 1:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.13a","order":"03.14.004.21366"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.14a","order":"03.14.004.21368"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.10"},"2 Tim. 4:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.24"},"Philem. 1:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.15a","order":"03.14.004.21370"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.1"},"Col. 2:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.11"},"Rev. 1:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.16a","order":"03.14.004.21372"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-lost"},"TG Scriptures, Lost"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.17a","order":"03.14.004.21374"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.2"},"Philem. 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.18a","order":"03.14.004.21376"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/3.17"},"2 Thes. 3:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.18b","order":"03.14.004.21378"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/13.3"},"Heb. 13:3"],"."]]}
